clips.title: Thank You For Everything: A Heartfelt Stream Recap
clips.hook: DaveyNT gets real about his mental state and expresses deep gratitude to his community for their unwavering support.

clips.title: Pro Tips: How to Track Monsters in Horror Games!
clips.hook: DaveyNT breaks down the audio cues for tracking the terrifying monsters in Elisa's Dollhouse. Learn how to survive!

clips.title: DaveyNT's Honest Horror Game Reaction!
clips.hook: Think you're tough playing horror games? DaveyNT admits his true reaction and why he does it!

clips.title: Unexpected Birthday Gift on Stream!
clips.hook: Watch DaveyNT's heartfelt reaction to a surprise birthday gift from a viewer, showing true community spirit!
